When you tuck your infant to sleep make sure that you provide proper support for their wobbly head. Children tend to develop a condition called flattening of the head due to sleeping in one constant position. This can be overcome by using a soft baby pillow. The Sunbaby Baby Pillow will help you preserve the adorable round form of your newborn’s head. This comfortable and soft pillow that is designed in the shape of Mickey mouse’s head will make a great visual appeal. With pictures of Walt Disney Mickey Mouse and Pluto printed on the pillow it will attract your baby’s attention.

You can use this pillow regularly for your newborns and thus help them sleep in the right posture that will give them comfortable sleep and ample rest. With dimensions of 28 x 28 cm this Sunbaby Baby Pillow can be used for children since birth.
